<h2>Why Oura charges a subscription and its rivals don't</h2>
<p>Oura Ring's subscription model funds the continuous development of its AI algorithm, which is constantly updated. Competitors have opted for a one-time payment model with more limited features but no monthly commitment.</p>
<p>The real question is: how much is it worth to you to receive personalized insights and tailored recommendations vs simply seeing raw data?</p>
